This repo contains an eclipse project.

The usage of the Zend PDT is recommend. The PDT contains all the required plugins for PHP developers.

Download at: http://www.zend.com/community/pdt/downloads

----------------
Project-Dir:
de.bht.fb6.mme2.mfg
| - lib (contains Zend Framework 2.1)
| - public (the only dir which should be accessible via HTTP)
| - module 
  | - MfgTestModul (our first small test module -> call /public/hello/world to see, how the world action in the hello controller reacts

